From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: experintellia <280144245+experintellia@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 09:21:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 08/13] wasm: file-based backup export/import

- tar streaming via vendored astral-tokio-tar fork whose tokio dep is
  the tokio-wasm-shim facade (memfs-backed fs on wasm)
- Sql::import wasm variant: sqlite-wasm-rs has no sqlcipher_export, so
  close the pool and swap the DB file bytes in the VFS instead
  (encrypted backups stay unsupported on wasm)
- scheduler stop: TaskTracker/timeout path cfg-gated for wasm
- delete_file routes through the memfs shim
